PostgreSQL

1.open source
2.Uses sql query language
3.use case - financial and health care applications

4. data types -  from primitive (integer,real,varChar)

5.data integrity - UNIQUE,NOT NULL


Where it’s used:

Web applications (backend databases).

Financial systems (because of strong data integrity).

Data warehousing & analytics.

Geospatial data (with PostGIS extension).

👉 In short: PostgreSQL = Reliable + Powerful + Flexible database, often considered the “most advanced open-source database in the world.”